      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been kept in a garage its whole life. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
